&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;One of the main items I wanted a Blog site for, is to share code I create.  I could just create a Public Github repository, but that just isn&amp;rsquo;t as pleasing to the eyes as a personal Blog can be.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The first person I know that created a Hugo site is &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://adminwillie.github.io/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;AdminWillie&lt;/a&gt;. I met him at the Central PA VMUG meetings and I also started attending the Blair County Little Hacks that he organizes. A great example of the vCommunity sharing ideas.&lt;/p&gt;
